(1, 1, 'GE 18.1 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in White', 'Want it delivered to your home? Search Internet #203547879. GE Profile products offer the best in contemporary design matched with the latest in appliance technology to transform the way you live. Energy Star qualified appliances feature a bold, dramatic look and state of the art features. This collection provides the perfect combination of style and innovation throughout your kitchen.\r\n\r\n\r\nWant it delivered to your home? Search Internet #203547879\r\nClick here to learn more about GE Appliances\r\nAdjustable spill-resistant glass shelves - Shelves are designed to keep spills from creating bigger messes\r\nClear crisper drawers - Transparent drawers make finding your favorite snacks quick and easy\r\nSnack drawer - Conveniently stores favorite foods and allows for quick, easy access\r\nGallon door storage - Milk and larger items are easily accommodated in the door\r\nCan storage door shelf - Holds soft drink cans in the door for easy selection and quick access\r\nWire freezer shelf - A sturdy shelf provides additional storage for frozen foods\r\nNeverclean condenser - Sealed compartment keeps coils clean and simplifies maintenance\r\nFresh food cabinet shelves 2 total - glass, 2 adjustable, 2 full-width, spill-resistant\r\nFresh food door shelves 3 fixed (2 with Gal. Storage)\r\nFresh food cabinet drawers 3 total clear, 1 snack drawer, 2 adjustable humidity crispers\r\nLeveling system 2 point front adjustable\r\nEco Options : Eco Options\r\nMFG Brand Name : GE\r\nMFG Model # : GTH18GBDWW\r\nMFG Part # : GTH18GBDWW', 599, 419, '2012-08-08 07:27:40', '2012-08-08 07:27:40', 'e58b155e-b486-46f5-98b6-4312b0da97f7_300.jpg', NULL, 1, 0),
(2, 1, 'Maytag 20.6 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Black', 'Combine efficiency and capacity in a top-freezer refrigerator. This ENERGY STAR qualified refrigerator helps you save money on utility bills. The convenient ice maker produces fresh ice in the freezer, eliminating the need to refill ice cube trays. Plus, it''s installed at the factory, so there''s no need to purchase a kit. A full-width Spill-Catcher glass shelf provides plenty of room for extra-wide items, while the FreshLock humidity controlled crispers help preserve the freshness of vegetables and fruit.\r\n\r\n\r\nCLICK HERE to learn more about Maytag Appliances\r\nENERGY STAR qualified and CEE Tier I rated, to help you save money on utility bills, use less energy and help preserve our natural resources\r\nFactory-installed icemaker eliminates the need to fill ice trays and helps you have a steady supply of ice on hand\r\nTemperature control is located at the top of the refrigerator compartment. A single knob controls the temperature in both the refrigerator and freezer compartments\r\nCool Flow ventilation: vents in the fresh food and freezer compartments circulate cold air around large items\r\nAdjustable Spill-Catcher glass shelves help contain spills for quick and easy cleanup\r\nFreshLock humidity controlled crispers help preserve the freshness of fruits and vegetables\r\nAdjustable gallon-sized refrigerator compartment door bins for flexible loading and quick cleaning\r\n14.4 cu. ft. fresh food compartment and 6.2 cu. ft. freezer compartment provide spacious storage options\r\nFull-width freezer shelf and 2 freezer door shelves help keep your freezer organized\r\nReversible door can open from the left or the right to fit into most kitchen spaces\r\nRefrigerator compartment''s incandescent lighting makes finding items easy\r\nEco Options : Eco Options\r\nMFG Brand Name : Maytag\r\nMFG Model # : M1TXEGMYB\r\nMFG Part # : M1TXEGMYB', 764, 535, '2012-08-08 07:31:36', '2012-08-08 07:31:36', '5dd0d