(3, 1, 'Summit Appliance 10.18 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel', 'SUMMIT offers frost-free refrigerator-freezers with slim dimensions for smaller kitchens and superior construction for years of reliable service. The FF1325SS has one of the largest interior capacities in the industry to fit into a 24 in. footprint. Adjustable glass shelves and full door racks in both compartments provide users with plenty of storage options to accommodate all sorts of items. The deluxe interior includes an extra-large freezer, interior lighting, and crisper. Frost-free operation guarantees quality cooling with minimum maintenance. Energy efficient and fully featured, the FF1325SS has a platinum cabinet and a fingerprint-proof stainless steel door. Its modern style makes this unit an elegant addition to any home kitchen with limited space but high standards.\r\n\r\n\r\nExtremely narrow width fits into even the tightest spaces\r\nStainless steel door brings modern style into the kitchen\r\nLarge capacity meets all your storage needs\r\nFull frost-free operation saves you maintenance\r\nAdjustable glass shelves offer flexible storage solutions\r\nCrisper drawer with humidity controls is ideal for preserving greens\r\nDoor racks offer convenient storage for cans and condiments\r\nReversible doors provide flexible placement options\r\nInterior light automatically illuminates when the door is opened\r\nLarge freezer section includes two door shelves\r\n**This product is excluded from Major Appliance Free Delivery and Haul Away promotion**\r\nMFG Brand Name : Summit Appliance\r\nMFG Model # : FF1325SS\r\nMFG Part # : FF1325SS', 829, 580, '2012-08-08 07:32:38', '2012-08-08 07:32:38', 'b3726960-47d8-4bfb-84df-01507d2e9257_300.jpg', NULL, 1, 1),
(4, 1, 'Hampton Bay Glendale 52 in. Oil Rubbed Bronze Ceiling Fan', 'The Hampton Bay Glendale 52 in. Ceiling Fan features an oil-rubbed bronze finish and 5 reversible dark teak/walnut blades for a handsome transitional look that complements a variety of home decor. The 3-light kit comes with light amber glass and uses three 13-watt CFL bulbs, included. The fan offers 3-speed reversible control so you can easily control the speed and airflow, and the multi-capacitor provides quiet operation.\r\n\r\n\r\n5 reversible dark teak/walnut blades allow you to change your decor style without replacing the entire unit\r\n3-light kit with light amber glass\r\n3-speed reversible control\r\nOil-rubbed bronze finish for a transitional style\r\nDesigned for interior use\r\nUses three 13-watt CFL bulbs, included\r\nMulti-capacitor offers quiet operation\r\nUp to 5,450 CFM airflow\r\nLarge room: room size up to 20 ft. x 20 ft.\r\nUL listed\r\nMFG Brand Name : Hampton Bay\r\nMFG Model # : AG524-ORB\r\nMFG Part # : AG524-ORB', 70, 49, '2012-08-08 07:34:23', '2012-08-08 07:34:23', '9ee836b1-c5bc-43fa-9403-4643d54da6a1_300.jpg', NULL, 1, 1),
