(6, 1, 'Hampton Bay Littleton 42 in. Ceiling Fan', 'The Littleton 42 in. Ceiling Fan features a white finish with 4 reversible white/bleached oak blades and a schoolhouse light kit with a frosted-glass globe shade for a transitional look that complements a variety of decor styles. The fan is ideal for use in rooms up to 10 ft. x 10 ft. in size and offers 3-speed reversible operation to help you easily select the desired speed and direction.\r\n\r\n\r\n4 reversible white/bleached oak blades make it easy to change your decor style without replacing the entire unit\r\nSingle-light schoolhouse light kit with frosted glass\r\n3-speed reversible operation\r\nWhite finish complements a variety of decor styles\r\nDesigned for interior use\r\nUses one 13-watt CFL bulb, included\r\nUp to 3,600 CFM airflow\r\nFor small room sizes up to 10 ft. x 10 ft.\r\nFlush-mount installation\r\nLight kit is not optional\r\nUL listed\r\nMFG Brand Name : Hampton Bay\r\nMFG Model # : UB42S-WH-SH\r\nMFG Part # : UB42S-WH-SH', 26, 18, '2012-08-08 07:36:36', '2012-08-08 07:36:36', 'c14b19b8-37d1-429d-9cf7-ce78058b1edf_300.jpg', NULL, 1, 0),
(7, 1, 'LG Electronics 3.6 cu. ft. High Efficiency Front Load Steam Washer in Graphite Steel', 'The LG Electronics 3.6 cu. ft. (DOE) Front Load Steam Washer features 9 wash programs, including delicates, cotton/normal, hand wash/wool and Speed Wash, for worry-free fabric care. The electronic control panel on the washer has an easy-to-read LED display and Dial-A-Cycle to make it easy to find the right setting. The washer''s Allergiene cycle helps reduce more than 95% of common household allergens, such as dust mites and domestic animal dander. This washer is Energy Star qualified for year-round energy and money savings.\r\n\r\n\r\nThe extra large 3.6 cu. ft. (DOE) capacity means fewer loads, saving time and energy, plus the extra large door opening makes it easy to load and unload your laundry\r\nElectronic control panel with LED display - Intuitive Dial-A-Cycle controls and easy to read LED display indicators help you find the right setting every time for you laundry needs\r\nColdWash technology uses cold water and enhanced washing motions to deliver cold-water savings with a warm-water performance\r\nGet your clothes cleaner and give them a longer life with revolutionary 6Motion technology, combines up to 6 different wash motions to work harder than ever to knock out dirt without being hard on fabrics\r\n9 wash programs: Allergiene, sanitary, bulky/large, cotton/normal, perm press, delicates, hand wash/wool, speed wash, tub clean, match loads for worry free and optimal fabric care\r\nLG Washers are Energy Star qualified and meet Consortium for Energy Efficiency Standards for a Tier III Rating, doing their important part for the environment\r\nThe NeveRust stainless steel drum resists rust and offers durability\r\nSteam deeply penetrates fabrics to knock out dirt and reduce wrinkles and odors while it also uses less water than traditional washers, so you won''t take a bath on your bills\r\nThe Allergiene cycle uses the power of steam to gently remove over 95% of common household allergens, like dust mites and pet dander, from even the most delicate fabrics\r\nTrueBalance anti-vibration system is designed to minimize washer vibration for smooth, quiet performance in any room of the house - even on the 2nd floor\r\nThe SenseClean wash system sets the water and washes time automatically based on the weight and size of each load for optimal washing care\r\nThe SpeedWash Cycle can have clothes clean and fresh quickly, when you just do not have time to wait\r\nMFG Brand Name : LG Electronics\r\nMFG Model # : WM2655HVA\r\nMFG Part # : WM2655HVA', 899, 629, '2012-08-08 07:39:13', '2012-08-08 07:39:13', 'cb49ca21-6218-4744-a5cb-66fecae32f59_300.jpg', NULL, 1, 0),
(8, 1, 'GE 4.1 cu. ft. DOE High-Efficiency Front Load Washer in White', 'The GE 4.1 cu. ft. Front Load Washer uses reversing tumble wash action to gently lift then drop clothes into the wash water solution, helping you achieve a thorough cleansing with less wear on fabrics. This Energy Star qualified washer has an eWash option that uses a cold water wash on select cycles to help deliver great washing action without sacrificing performance. The washer''s HydroHeater internal water heater boosts incoming water temperatures to help brighten whites while helping eliminate common bacteria.\r\n\r\n\r\nCLICK HERE to learn more about GE Washers\r\n4.1 cu. ft. washer handles large loads to help you spend less time in the laundry room\r\nReversing tumble wash action gently lifts then drops the load into the wash water solution for thorough cleansing with less wear on fabrics\r\nHydroheater internal water heater boosts incoming water temperatures to help brighten whites while helping eliminate common bacteria\r\n1,200 rpm spin speed helps remove water efficiently to minimize dry time\r\n11 wash cycles, including heavy-duty, hand washable and delicates cycles, help you care properly for a wide range of fabrics\r\nStain Wash cycle is designed to fight tough stains and provide a deep, thorough clean\r\nSpeed Wash Cycle delivers a quick wash for lightly soiled items that are needed in a hurry\r\nRinse-and-spin cycle offers a fast, convenient way to remove odors and residue from items like swimsuits and towels\r\neWash option uses a cold water wash on select cycles without sacrificing performance\r\nEnergy star qualified to meet or exceed federal guidelines for energy efficiency for year-round energy and money savings\r\nStainless steel tub is durable\r\nEco Options : Eco Options\r\nMFG Brand Name : GE\r\nMFG Model # : GFWH2400LWW\r\nMFG Part # : GFWH2400LWW', 809, 566, '2012-08-08 07:40:04', '2012-08-08 07:40:04', 'e6180ccd-3125-48a0-bf63-36c53af4ba17_300.jpg', NULL, 1, 0),
